Tourist trap
Aug 2015
People frequently visit Ha Long Bay as it one of the top tourist spots in Vietnam, however, since it has become popular, it is becoming less clean and overrun with tourists. If you are looking for a more unique and interesting experience, consider Cat Ba island instead. It has similar rock formations in the bay, but less crowded.
